      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 212,
      "message": "The right way to log it is LOGGER.error(\"Catalog notification on VSP IDs '{}', action '{}' failed\", itemIds, action, e);\n\nThis is the correct platform for SLF4J, and including \"e\" will print the stack trace (as opposed to e.getMessage(), which can be empty or null).",
